Class AbstractSerializerAdapter

java.lang.Object

      org.eclipse.jst.ws.jaxws.dom.runtime.persistence.serializer.AbstractSerializerAdapter
All Implemented Interfaces:
org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Adapter, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Adapter.Internal, IAnnotationSerializer
Direct Known Subclasses:
MethodSerializerAdapter, ParameterSerializerAdapter, SeiSerializerAdapter, WsSerializerAdapter
public abstract class AbstractSerializerAdapter
extends org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.impl.AdapterImpl
implements IAnnotationSerializer

Base class for DOM adapters that listen to changes in DOM objects and applies it to the underlying java class. Extenders should implement getAnnotation() method to provide the IAnnotation instance to be saved to java class.

Author:
Georgi Vachkov
